SELECT id, CHAR_LENGTH(GROUP_CONCAT(body)) AS l FROM (SELECT 'a' AS id, REPEAT('foo bar', 100) AS body UNION ALL SELECT 'a' AS id, REPEAT('bla bla', 100) AS body) t1 GROUP BY id ORDER BY l DESC
